        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3232383281?book_show_action=true">Mar 27, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carrie Shields" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carrie Shields" href="/user/show/38783540-carrie-shields">Carrie Shields</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3232383281" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7370184422158150430">This was a book I took my time with and savored. The writing was so smart and so suspenseful that I didn&apos;t want the book to end. I tried to think of authors I could compare Sharon to and came up empty as her voice is uniquely her own. If you have not read THE ASSOCIATION, you are truly missing out on a wonderful literary experience.</span>
  <span id="freeText7370184422158150430" style="display:none">This was a book I took my time with and savored. The writing was so smart and so suspenseful that I didn't want the book to end. I tried to think of authors I could compare Sharon to and came up empty as her voice is uniquely her own. If you have not read THE ASSOCIATION, you are truly missing out on a wonderful literary experience.</span>
